  <h3>Cloud Engineer and Hardware Nerd</h3>
  <p>
    I am a Cloud Engineer working on AWS, Azure, Infrastructure & Automation, and GitOps / Kubernetes. 
    I like to continuously expand my knowledge using my HomeLab environment to deploy and experiment with open source technologies.
  </p>
  <p>
    My motto: "Boil things down to the most fundamental truths and reason up from there."
  </p>
  {/* <Button title='Sponsor Me' class='w-fit' href='/projects#sponsorship' variant='ahead' /> */}

